WEBVTT

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:02.080
And in the middle is my mother, Marion.

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:05.656
She was sent to start a new life

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:07.176
in a new country

00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:08.456
on her own

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:09.920
at the age of 12.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:12.536
I know this:

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.816
if Britain had not admitted refugees

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:17.040
in the 1940s,

00:01:17.800 --> 00:01:20.880
I certainly would not be here today.

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:26.360
Yet 70 years on,
the wheel has come full circle.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:29.856
The sound is of walls being built,

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:32.376
vengeful political rhetoric,